title: Carlos Meza
text: I am an Assistant Professor of Data Analytics and Genomics at the Department of Industrial Engineering, Universidad del Norte, Barranquilla, Colombia. My research interests include applied analytics, bioinformatics, population genetics and Machine Learning.
